    <item>
      <title>Firewall Configuration</title>
      <link>/klaytn-cypress-setup-workshop/10_prerequisites/10_firewall_configuration.html</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Jul 2022 19:18:45 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>/klaytn-cypress-setup-workshop/10_prerequisites/10_firewall_configuration.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;1-only-for-cn-firewall-configuration&#34;&gt;1. &lt;em&gt;(Only for CN)&lt;/em&gt; Firewall configuration&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;1-if-baobab-validation-is-completed-remove-below-klaytn-cns-ip-addresses-of-baobab-from-your-firewall-configuration&#34;&gt;1) If Baobab validation is completed, remove below Klaytn CN&amp;rsquo;s IP addresses of Baobab from your firewall configuration.&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;54.180.180.202&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;54.180.18.176&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;52.79.134.72&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;52.78.232.39&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;2-for-communication-and-multichannel-across-cco-cns-in-the-cypress-network-tcp-32323-32324-and-udp--32323--from-existing-ccos-cns-should-be-allowed-in-your-cn-firewall-configuration&#34;&gt;2) For communication and multichannel across CCO CNs in the Cypress network, TCP &lt;code&gt;32323-32324&lt;/code&gt; and UDP &lt;code&gt;32323&lt;/code&gt; from existing CCO&amp;rsquo;s CNs should be allowed in your CN firewall configuration.&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;** The existing CCO&amp;rsquo;s CNs IP addresses will be provided by Slack DM.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Package Installation</title>
      <link>/klaytn-cypress-setup-workshop/10_prerequisites/20_package_installation.html</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Jul 2022 19:18:57 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>/klaytn-cypress-setup-workshop/10_prerequisites/20_package_installation.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;2-installation-of-klaytn-packages-for-cn-and-pn&#34;&gt;2. Installation of Klaytn packages for CN and PN&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;** We&amp;rsquo;ve already installed packages during the Pre-cypress stage. If you need to install newly, please refer these documents.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;1-document-pages&#34;&gt;1) Document pages&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CN - &lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.kaia.io/nodes/core-cell/install/install-consensus-nodes/&#34;&gt;https://docs.kaia.io/nodes/core-cell/install/install-consensus-nodes/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;PN - &lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.kaia.io/nodes/core-cell/install/install-proxy-nodes/&#34;&gt;https://docs.kaia.io/nodes/core-cell/install/install-proxy-nodes/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;2-reinstall-knd-caused-by-version-conflict&#34;&gt;2) Reinstall k*nd caused by version conflict&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo su&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ cd /tmp&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ cp /etc/k*nd/conf/k*nd.conf /tmp&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ systemctl stop k*nd&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo rm -rf /var/cache/yum&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo rm /etc/yum.repos.d/klaytn.repo&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo curl -o /etc/yum.repos.d/kaia.repo https://packages.kaia.io/config/rhel/7/kaia.repo&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo yum list k*nd&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ yum remove k*nd -y&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo yum install k*nd-v1.0.2-0.el7&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ cp k*nd.conf /etc/k*nd/conf/&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ systemctl start k*nd&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ k*n version&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;If you finish this step, please click the next button &lt;code&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; on the right side of this page.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
